I / O Ext ZhuHai night special live post a summary post to the ......
Tang concert on June 25 ended successfully as early as 3:00&lt;br&gt;

And people around the world concerned about Google's new technology for the first time released&lt;br&gt;
Opportunity to finally provide technical enthusiasts a night long conversation really do, eat together, drink together, sleep together, watching live&lt;br&gt;
I hope to bring everyone shines new technology works with Google&lt;br&gt;

This year I / O conference highlights:&lt;br&gt;
AndroidOne plan&lt;br&gt;
AndroidOne is a program for developing markets. Through a wide range of optional components designed to create high-quality, low-cost smartphone.&lt;br&gt;

Android L system&lt;br&gt;
The system uses a new design, with simple buttons, rounded font application icon and a new, multi-task switching to a card stack effect, the default runtime environment using ART, fully compatible with 64-bit mobile processor, using the precompiled approach will make Android the system run more smoothly, the new increase 5000 new API. Android L system is the official version will be launched this fall.&lt;br&gt;

Android Wear&lt;br&gt;
Google Android Wear a smart watch to create a new intelligent platform Android Wear.&lt;br&gt;
Google said it would publish the full Android Wear SDK, API consistent with the standard version of its Android API, developers porting applications do not exist difficulty.&lt;br&gt;


Android Auto&lt;br&gt;
Google released the Android Auto Assembly on-board systems to destabilize Apple's CarPlay, new AndroidAuto SDK contains a system similar to other Android Notification Center API interface allows developers to develop applications for the automobile.&lt;br&gt;

Android TV&lt;br&gt;
This is a Google user to occupy the living room of a product, it will be a platform product, the system can be used for television set-top boxes, there is a corresponding SDK, and not just the TV itself.&lt;br&gt;
Android TV is a dual-purpose platforms: television and games. It needs to be a voice control D Pad. In addition, users can also use Android Wear smart wristwatch device to control Android TV.&lt;br&gt;

Google Fit&lt;br&gt;
Google Fit through a series of API to manage collected from sensors, application of health data. Currently, Google Fit has a large number of partners, Adidas and Nike certainly will not be an exception.&lt;br&gt;

Google's cloud offerings&lt;br&gt;
Google Drive and Google cloud platform. Google Drive lets Microsoft has clearly felt the pressure:&lt;br&gt;

     Google Drive is now 30 days average number of active users has reached 190 million people or more.&lt;br&gt;
     The world's top 100 start-ups, the 67 converted from Microsoft Office to use Google products;&lt;br&gt;
     Fortune 500 companies, the 58% have switched to Google;&lt;br&gt;
     The world's top 100 universities, 72 have been put into the arms of Google.&lt;br&gt;

Participants welfare&lt;br&gt;
Conference final, Google said that all participants can get free LG G Watch or Samsung Gear Live smart watches, and after MOTO 360 released, Google will be presented to each participant. After returning everyone some playing Aunt&lt;br&gt;


